title: Trackmania Car Pack!
description:
this a a car pack for trackmania nations forever follow this intructions to get it working:


1) Download
2) DO NOT!!!!!! Unzip the files
3) Copy al the files to: C:/Documents/Trackmania/Skins/Vehicles/CarCommon(if the map not exist just create it)
4) Start Trackmania nations forever, select profile, and Vehicles, and all the new, cool cars are at the end of the list, select them to edit the or just drive them as they are

Some cars whitch I have included: 
Porshe 911
Dodge Viper
Seat Cupra GT
Audi RSQ Concept
TVR

And some fun stuff:
Monowheel ( just 1 wheel )
planes
And A Tractor/Bulldozer

So just download this!
